From Randy Davis Subject Re A Miracle in California In article seven egreen writes Bikers wave to bikers the world Whether or not Harley riders wave to other bikers is one of our favorite flame I am happy to say that some Harley riders in our area are better than most that are flamed about here I riding a lowly sport bike no less and my girlfriend were the recipient of no less than twenty waves from a group of at least twenty five Harley I was leading a group of about four sport bikes at the time I initiated some of the waves but not It was a perfect day and friendly riders despite some brand differences made it all the Randy Davis Email ZX Pilot uunet ucsd megatek randy DoD